   Bonds: Shearson Lehman Hutton Treasury index 3360.61, up
19.35.
   Commodities: Dow Jones futures index 133.47, off 0.68;
spot index 136.39, up 0.18.
   Dollar: 151.25 yen, up 1.85; 1.6740 marks, off 0.0084.
